owl:Ontology.dc:title: Unconstrained properties
owl:Ontology.dc:description: Properties that are derived from the elements of all of the RDA entities with semantics that are independent of the IFLA Library Reference Model.
owl:Ontology.dc:rights: Copyright © 2020 American Library Association, Canadian Federation of Library Associations, and CILIP: Chartered Institute of Library and Information Professionals
owl:Ontology.dc:creator: RDA Steering Committee

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has abbreviated title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a title that is abbreviated for purposes of indexing or identification.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har forkortet titel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en titel, der er forkortet mhp. indeksering eller identifikation.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abbreviated title of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a title of resource that has been abbreviated for purposes of indexing or identification.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridged as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that shortens a related resource without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er forkortet til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der forkorter en oprindelig ressource uden at ændre den overordnede betydning eller præsentationsmåde.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridgement of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is shortened as a related resoure without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er forkortelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet forkortet, dvs. afkortet, uden at der er ændret på en oprindelig ressources overordnede betydning eller præsentationsmåde.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has abridger
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who contributes to a resource by shortening an a related resource without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Substantial modification that results in the creation of a new resource is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har forkorter
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at forkorte eller komprimere en originalressource, men som i alt væsentligt har ladt originalens karakter og indhold uændret.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Væsentlige ændringer, der resulterer i skabelsen af en ny ressource, er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridger of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of shortening another resource without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er forkorter af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at forkorte eller komprimere den oprindelige ressource, men som i alt væsentligt har ladt den oprindelige ressources karakter og indhold være uændret til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has absorbed agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent who was absorbed by another agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har absorberet agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en agent, der var absorberet af en anden agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content incorporates the content of another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indlemmet af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der inkorporerer en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed in part by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content incorporates the partial content of another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er delvis indlemmet af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der delvis inkorporerer en anden ressources indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has absorbing agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent who absorbed another agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har indlemmende agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en agent, der indlemmede en anden agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorption in part of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose partial content is incorporated in the content of another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er delvis absorbering af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er delvis inkorporeret i en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorption of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content is incorporated in the content of another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er absorbering af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet inkorporeret i en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracted as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that abbreviates another resource in a brief, objective manner.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammenfattet som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der forkorter en oprindelig ressource på en kortfattet, objektiv måde.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracted in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that abstracts the contents of another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammenfattet i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er en abstracts- og indekseringsservice, der sammenfatter en oprindelig kildes indehold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstract of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is abbreviated in a brief, objective manner.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammenfatning af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er sammenfattet, dvs. forkortet på en kortfattet, objektiv måde.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracts for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is abstracted by another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammenfatninger af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, hvis indhold er blevet sammenfattet af en abstract- og indekseringsservice.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has academic degree
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a rank conferred as a guarantee of academic proficiency.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har akademisk grad
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en rang, der tildeles som garanti for akademisk færdighed.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has academic supervisor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for overseeing academic activity of any kind that results in a resource, including theses, research, and projects.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has accessibility content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an indication of the kinds of resource that provide alternative sensory modes to perceive the main resources that are embodied by an augmentation aggregate.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Accessibility content includes accessible labels, audio description, captioning, image description, sign language, and subtitles. Accessibility content does not include subtitles in a language different from the spoken content.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har tilgængelighedsfremmende indhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en indikation af indhold, der giver alternative sansemåder for at forstå en ressources primære indhold.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Omfatter lydbeskrivelser, rubrikker, billedbeskrivelser, tegnsprog, og undertekster. Omfatter ikke undertekster på et andet sprog end det talte.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has access point for entity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an entity to an appellation of entity in natural language that is taken from a vocabulary encoding scheme or is constructed using a string encoding scheme.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is access point for entity of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to an entity that has an appellation in natural language that is taken from a vocabulary encoding scheme or is constructed using a string encoding scheme.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is accompanied by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is issued with a related resource, without any relationship to its content.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er ledsaget af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource udgivet sammen med en anden ressource uden nogen relation til dens indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has accompanying resource relationship with (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is an augmentation of, or is augmented by, or is complemented by, or accompanies, or is accompanied by a resource. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har ledsaget ressource-relation med
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er en berigelse af, eller er beriget af, eller er komplementeret af en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has actor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is a performer who contributes to a resource by acting as a cast member or player in a musical or dramatic presentation.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har skuespiller
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en performer, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at fungere som rolleindehaver eller aktør i en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is actor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of acting as a cast member or player in a musical or dramatic presentation.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er skuespiller i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en udøver, der bidrager til en ressource ved at være skuespiller eller musiker i en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation etc. til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is modified for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies to changes in form or to resources completely rewritten in the same form.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet ændret til et andet formål, en anden brug eller et andet medium end det, det oprindeligt var beregnet til.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Gælder for ændringer i form eller for ressourcer, der er omskrevet fuldstændigt i samme form.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that modifies another resource for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies to changes in form or to resources completely rewritten in the same form.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der modificerer en oprindelig ressource til et andet formål, en anden brug eller et andet medium end det, det oprindeligt var beregnet til.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation gælder for ændringer i form eller for ressourcer, der er omskrevet fuldstændigt i samme form.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as choreography
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a choreographic resource based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til koreografi
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af bevægelse baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as graphic novel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a graphic novel based on another resource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til graphic novel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en graphic novel baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as libretto
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical or choreographic resource such as an opera, a ballet, or other resource for the musical stage, or an oratorio
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til libretto
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af tekst til en opera eller en anden ressource for den musikalske scene eller et oratorium baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as motion picture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a motion picture that is based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet som film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en film baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as motion picture screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of a screenplay for a motion picture, based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet som film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af en drejebog til en film, baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as musical theatre
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical theatre resource based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til musikteater
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en musikteater-ressource baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as novel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a novel adapted from another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbjdet til roman
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en roman bearbejdet ud fra en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as opera
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an opera based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til opera
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en opera baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as oratorio
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an oratorio based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til oratorium
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et oratorium baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as radio program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a radio program based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til radioprogram (udtryk)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et radioprogram baseret på et oprindeligt udtryk.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as radio script
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of a script for a radio program, based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til radiomanuskript
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af et manuskript til et radioprogram, baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of a screenplay for a motion picture, television program, or video, based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet som drejebog
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af et manuskript til en film, et tv-program eller en video, baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as television program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a television program based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til tv-program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et TV-program baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as television screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of a screenplay for a television program, based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til tv-manuskript
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af et manuskript til et tv-program, baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a video based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til video
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en video baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video game
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to relates a resource to a video game based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet som computerspil
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en videospilsressource baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of a screenplay for a video, based on another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til videomanuskript
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af et manuskript til en video, baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted in verse as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a literary composition in verse form adapted from another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: bearbejdet i versform som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en litterær komposition i versform, bearbejdet ud fra en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has addenda
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of brief content that is essential for the completeness of a related resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er tillæg
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af kortfattet indhold, som er væsentligt for fuldstændigheden af en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addenda to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content is completed with brief content from a related resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er tillæg til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, hvortil der er tilføjet kortfattet ekstra materiale fra en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has additional scale information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an indication of supplemental information about scale.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Statement of comparative measurements or limitation of the scale to particular parts of the content of a resource are included.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har supplerende målestoksforhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en indikation af supplerende oplysninger om målestoksforhold.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Supplerende målestoksforhold omfatter angivelse i flere måleenheder eller som begrænsning af målestoksforholdet til visse dele af ressourcen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has addressee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent to whom a resource or part of a resource is addressed.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har adressat
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, som en ressource eller en del af en ressource er adresseret til.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addressee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource or a portion of a resource that is addressed to an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er adressat i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, som en ressource eller en del af en ressource er adresseret til til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has address of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an address of an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har adresse på agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressourcetil en agents bopælsadresse, forretningsadresse eller arbejdsgivers adresse og/eller en e-mail- eller internetadresse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has affiliation (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a group with which an agent is affiliated or is affiliated through employment, membership, cultural identity, etc. (Deprecation)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har tilhørsforhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en gruppe, som en agent er eller har været tilknyttet via beskæftigelse, medlemskab, kulturel identitet etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has agent history
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to biographical or historical information about an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har agenthistorie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til biografiske eller historiske oplysninger om en agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is aggregated by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that aggregates a resource as part of the plan of an aggregating resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: aggregates
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is chosen as part of the plan of an aggregating resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has aggregator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for creating an aggregating resource by selecting and arranging other resources.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is aggregator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for aggregation by selecting and arranging other resources.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is also issued as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that carries the same content of a resource in a different format.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er også udgivet som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der omfatter det samme indehold af en ressource i et andet format.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has alternate identity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a nomen that is a pseudonym or other appellation used by an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har alternativ identitet
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en pseudonym eller anden identitet antaget af en person til en agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is alternate identity of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to an agent who has an appellation of agent that is a pseudonym or other assumed identity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysed in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that describes the structure and composition of another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er analyseret i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der undersøger en oprindelig ressource for at identificere dets dele og deres relationer.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysis of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose structure is described by a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er analyse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet undersøgt for at identificere dets bestanddele og deres relationer.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has animator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who contributes to a resource by giving apparent movement to inanimate objects or drawings.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Creation of the drawings that are animated is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har animator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource af et levende billedværk eller et computerprogram ved at give en illusion af bevægelse til livløse genstande eller tegninger.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Skabelse af tegninger, der er animeret, er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is animator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of giving apparent movement to inanimate objects or drawings.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Creation of the drawings that are animated is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er animator til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der der har bidraget til en levende billed-ressource eller et computerprogram ved at give en illusion af bevægelse til livløse genstande eller tegninger til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has annotator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who adds notes and other information to a resource by hand.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har annotationsskriver
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der laver manuskriptnotater på et eksemplar.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is annotator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that carries notes and other information added by hand.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er annotationsforfatter i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der skriver annotationer i hånden på en ressource til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who appeals a decision of a lower court recorded in a legal resource of a higher court.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har appellerende
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent der gør indsigelse mod en underrets beslutning, der er registreret i et juridisk værk fra en højere retsinstans.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellant of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource of a higher court recording a decision of a lower court that is appealed by an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er appellerende af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der appellerer en underrets beslutning i en juridisk ressource til en højere retsinstans til et værk.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellation of entity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an entity to a nomen that is used within a given scheme or context to refer to an entity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellation of entity of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to an entity that is referred to by a nomen used within a given scheme or context.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent against whom an appeal is taken on a decision of a lower court recorded in a legal resource of a higher court.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har indstævnet
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource mod hvilken en indsigelse er gjort gennem en underrets beslutning, der er registreret i en juridisk ressource fra en højere retsinstans.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a legal resource of a higher court that records a decision of a lower court that appeals against an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indstævnet af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent mod hvem der er gjort indsigelse over en underrets beslutning, der er registreret i en juridisk ressource fra en højere retsinstans til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appendix
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content augments a related resource.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der udgør en berigende del af en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appendix to

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has applied material

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for an architectural design, including a pictorial representation intended to show how a building or other structure will look when completed.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is architect of

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er arkitekt til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have skabt et arkitektonisk design, inkl. en billedrepræsentation, der er beregnet til at vise, hvordan en bygning etc. vil se ud, når den er færdig til et værk.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is arranged as

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is arrangement of

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er arrangement af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en musikressource, der er blevet omskrevet til en anden besætning end den, ressourcen oprindeligt var beregnet til.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has arranger of music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who contributes to a resource by rewriting a composition for a medium of performance different from that for which a resource was originally intended.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Modification of the resource for the same medium of performance, etc., keeping the musical substance of the original composition essentially unchanged, is included. Substantial modification that results in the creation of a new musical resource is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har musikarrangør
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til en musikressource ved at omskrive kompositionen til en anden besætning end den, ressourcen oprindeligt var beregnet til.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Bidrag omfatter ændring af en ressource for den samme besætning etc., der i alt væsentligt bevarer den originale kompositions musikalske substans uændret, og omfatter ikke væsentlige ændringer der resulterer i skabelsen af en ny musikressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is arranger of music of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of rewriting a musical composition for a medium of performance different from that for which the resource was originally intended.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musikarrangør af

Colour content applies to a resource with a content type of "cartographic image", "cartographic moving image", "cartographic three-dimensional form", "notated movement", "notated music", "performed movement", "still image", "text", "three-dimensional moving image", "three-dimensional form", or "two-dimensional moving image".

rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Content type also reflects the number of spatial dimensions and the presence or absence of movement in which content expressed in the form of an image or images is intended to be perceived.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has derivative
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a modification of another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er afledning
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er en ændring af en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has derivative resource relationship with (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is based on or is a derivative of a related resource. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har afledt ressource-relation med
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er baseret på eller er en afledning af en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is described in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an entity to a resource that describes a entity.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er beskrevet i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der beskriver en beskreven entitet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is description of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an entity that is described by a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er beskrivelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der beskrives af en beskrivende entitet.
Relates a resource to a resource that is described in or is a description of the resource. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has descriptive resource relationship with (Deprecated)
has designation of edition
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character or group of words or characters, identifying an edition to which a resource belongs.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har udgavebetegnelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et ord, tegn eller en gruppe af ord og/eller tegn, der identificerer en udgave som en ressource tilhører.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has designation of named revision of edition
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character or group of words or characters, identifying a particular revision of a named edition.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har betegnelse for en navngivet revision af en udgave
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et ord, tegn eller en gruppe af ord og/eller tegn, der identificerer en bestemt revision af en navngiven udgave.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has designation of version
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word or phrase that distinguishes a resource from another resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for creating a design for an object.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for ideen bag designet for et objekt.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is designer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for design of an object.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er designer af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have skabt et design for en genstand til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of applied material
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a physical or chemical substance applied to a base material of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om anvendt materiale
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om et fysisk eller kemisk stof, der er påført en ressources basismateriale.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of aspect ratio designation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a ratio of the width to the height of a moving image.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om billedformatbetegnelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om forholdet mellem bredde og højde i et levende billede.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of base material
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of an underlying physical material of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om basismateriale
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om en ressources underliggende fysiske materiale til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of bibliographic format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the proportional relationship between a whole sheet in a printed or manuscript resource, and the individual leaves that result if that sheet is left full, cut, or folded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om bogformat
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om resultatet af at folde et trykt ark, så der dannes en samling af blade.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of broadcast standard
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a system used to format a video resource for television broadcast.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om transmissionsstandard
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om system, der anvendes til at formatere en videoressource til tv-transmission

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an indication of mathematical data and other features of the cartographic content of a resource not recorded in statements of scale, projection, and coordinates.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har andre detaljer om kartografisk indhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en indikation af matematiske data og andre karakteristika ved en ressources kartografiske indhold, der ikke er registreret som del af målestoks-, projicerings- eller koordinatoplysninger.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of cartographic data type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a machine-readable representation of geospatial features.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om kartografisk datatype
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om en maskinlæsbar repræsentation af geospatiale træk.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of colour content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a presence of colour, tone, etc., in the content of a resource, and the specific colours, tones, etc., including black and white, present.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om farveindhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om tilstedeværelse af farve, nuance etc. i en ressources indhold, samt de specifikke farver, nuancer etc., inkl. sort og hvid, der er til stede.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of configuration of playback channels
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a number of sound channels used to make a recording.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om konfiguration af afspilningskanaler
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om et antal af lydkanaler, der blev anvendt til en indspilning

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of digital file characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a technical specification relating to a digital encoding of text, image, audio, video, and other types of data in a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om digitale filkarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om teknisk specifikation relateret til den digitale kodning af tekst, billede, audio-, video- og andre datatyper i en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of digital representation of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of an encoding of geospatial information in a cartographic resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om digital repræsentation af kartografisk indhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om kodning af geospatiale oplysningerer i en kartografisk ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of duration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to aetails of an extent of resource that is a playing time, performance time, running time, or other length of time.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om spilletid
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om varighed, spilletid, opførelsestid etc. for en ressources indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of emulsion on microfilm and microfiche
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a suspension of light-sensitive chemicals used as a coating on a microfilm or microfiche.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om emulsion på mikrofilm og mikrofiche
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om opslæmmede lysfølsomme kemikalier, der er anvendt som belægning på en mikrofilm eller mikrofiche

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of encoding format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a schema or standard used to encode the digital content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om kodningsformat
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om skema, standard etc., der anvendes til kodning af en ressources digitale indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of file type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a general type of data content encoded in a computer file.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om filtype
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om typen af dataindhold kodet i en computerfil.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of font size
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a size of the type used to represent characters and symbols in a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om skriftstørrelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om størrelsen på den skrifttype, der er anvendt til at repræsentere tegn og symboler i en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of format of notated music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a musical or physical layout of the content of a resource that is presented in a form of musical notation.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om format af noteret musik
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det musikalske eller fysiske layout af en ressources indhold, der er repræsenteret som musikalsk notation.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of form of musical notation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a set of characters or symbols used to express musical content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om musikalsk notationsform
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det tegnsæt og/eller symboler der anvendes for at udtrykke en ressources musikalske indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of form of notated movement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a set of characters or symbols used to express movement content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om bevægelsesnotationsform
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det sæt af tegn og/eller de symboler, der er anvendt til at udtrykke en ressources bevægelsesindhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of form of tactile notation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a set of characters or symbols used to express the content of a resource in a form that can be perceived through touch.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om taktil notationsform
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det tegnsæt og/eller symboler, der er anvendt til at udtrykke en ressources indhold på en måde, der kan opfattes ved berøring.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of generation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a relationship between an original carrier and a carrier of a reproduction made from an original.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om generation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om forholdet mellem en oprindelig bærer og bæreren af en reproduktion baseret på originalen.

Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original audio carrier and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a tape duplication master, a test pressing). (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of generation of audio recording (Deprecated)

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original carrier of a digital resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a derivative master).. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of generation of digital resource (Deprecated)

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of generation of microform (Deprecated)

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original carrier of a motion picture film resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a reference print).. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of generation of motion picture film (Deprecated)

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original carrier of a videotape resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a show copy).. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of generation of videotape (Deprecated)

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a groove width of an analog disc or a groove pitch of an analog cylinder.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om rillekarakteristika

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of illustrative content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of content intended to illustrate a primary content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om illustrativt indhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om indhold, der er beregnet til at illustrere et udtryks primære indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of layout
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of an arrangement of text, images, tactile notation, or other content in a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om layout
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om opstilling af tekst, billeder, taktil notation etc. i en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of mount
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a physical material used for the support or backing to which the base material of a resource is attached.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om montage
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det fysiske materiale, der udgør den støtte eller bagbeklædning, som en ressources basismateriale er fastgjort på.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of playing speed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a speed at which an audio carrier must be operated to produce the sound intended.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om omdrejningshastighed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om den hastighed, som en lydbærer skal betjenes ved for at producere den ønskede lyd.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of polarity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a relationship of the colours and tones in an image to the colours and tones of the object reproduced.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om polaritet
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om forholdet mellem farver og nuancer i et billede samt farver og nuancer i den reproducerede genstand.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of presentation format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a format used in the production of a projected image.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om fremvisningsformat
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det format, der er anvendt ved fremstillingen af et projiceret billede.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of production method
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a process used to produce a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om produktionsmetode
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om den proces, der er anvendt til at fremstille en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of production method for manuscript (Deprecated)

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a process used to produce a tactile resource. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of production method for tactile resource (Deprecated)
has details of projection characteristic of motion picture film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a technical specification relating to the projection of a motion picture film.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om projektionskarakteristika for film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om teknisk specifikation relateret til projektion af en film.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of projection speed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a speed at which a projected carrier must be operated to produce the moving image intended.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om projektionshastighed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om den hastighed, som en projiceret bærer skal betjenes ved for at producere det ønskede levende billede.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of recording medium
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a type of medium used to record sound on an audio carrier.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om optagemedie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det optagemedie, der er anvendt til at optage lyd på en lydbærer.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of reduction ratio designation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a general designation of the size of a micro-image in relation to the original from which it was produced.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om reduktionsforholdsbetegnelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om betegnelsen for størrelse på et mikrobillede i forhold til den original, som det er fremstillet ud fra.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a designation for one or more regions of the world for which a videodisc or video game carrier is encoded, indicating that playback is restricted to a device configured to decode it.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om en kode, der identificerer den region i verden, som en videodisc er kodet til, og som forhindrer, at videodiscen bliver spillet på en afspiller solgt i en anden region.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of script
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of set of characters or symbols used to express written language content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om skriftstørrelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det sæt af tegn og/eller de symboler, der er anvendt til at udtrykke en ressources skriftlige sprogindhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of sound characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a technical specification relating to the encoding of sound in a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om lydkarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressouce til detaljer om teknisk specifikation relateret til kodning af lyd i en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of special playback characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of an equalization system, noise-reduction system, or other processing that is used in making an audio recording.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om særlige afspilningskarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om et equalizersystem, støjdæmpningssystem etc., der er anvendt til at lave en lydoptagelse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of tape configuration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a number of tracks on an audiotape.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om båndkonfiguration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om antal spor på et lydbånd.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of track configuration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a configuration of the audio track on a sound-track film.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om lydsporskonfiguration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om konfiguration af lydsporet til en film med soundtrack.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of type of recording
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a method used to encode audio content for playback.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om indspilningskarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om den metode, der er anvendt til at kode lydindhold til afspilning.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of video characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a technical specification relating to an encoding of video images in a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om videokarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om teknisk specifikation relateret til kodning af videobilleder i en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of video format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a schema or standard used to encode the analog video content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om videoformat
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om standard etc., der anvendes til kodning af en ressources analoge videoindhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digested as

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammendraget som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der systematisk og gennemgribende komprimerer en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digest of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a systematic and comprehensive condensing of a related resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammendrag af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er et sammendrag, dvs. der er systematisk og gennemgribende komprimeret.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has digital file characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a technical specification relating to a digital encoding of text, image, audio, video, and other types of data in a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har digitale filkarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en teknisk specifikation relateret til den digitale kodning af tekst, billede, audio-, video- og andre datatyper i en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has digital representation of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a set of technical details relating to an encoding of geospatial information in a cartographic resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har digital repræsentation af kartografisk indhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et sæt af tekniske detaljer relateret til kodning af geospatiale oplysningerer i en kartografisk ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has digital transfer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource in a digital format that results from a transfer of a resource in another digital format.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har digital overførsel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource i et digitalt format, der er resultatet af en overførsel af en ressource i et andet digitalt format.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digital transfer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource in a digital format that is transferred to another digital format.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er digital overførsel af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource i et digitalt format, der er overført til et andet digitalt format.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dimensions
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a measurement of a carrier or a container of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har størrelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et mål for en ressources bærer eller dens opbevaringsudstyr.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dimensions of cartographic image
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a measurement of a face of a map, etc.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har størrelse på kort etc. - kartografi
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et mål for en billedside af et kort etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dimensions of still image
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a measurement of the pictorial area of a still image.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har størrelse på fast billede
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et mål for et fast billedes billedområde.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance, a radio or television program, etc.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har instruktør
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for ledelse af og tilsyn med en filmoptagelse, et radio- eller tv-program etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance, a radio or television program, etc.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er instruktør til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der er ansvarlig for ledelse af og tilsyn med en filmoptagelse, et radio- eller tv-program etc. til en ressource.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der tilfører udsmukning til en særlig ressource vha. ædelmetal eller farve, ofte med udsøgte mønstre og motiver.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illuminator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that is decorated using precious metals or colour, often with elaborate designs and motifs.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er illuminator af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en person der sørger for at der er tilført en udsmukning til en særlig ressource vha. ædelmetal eller farve, ofte med udsøgte mønstre og motiver til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has illustrations
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of pictorial content designed to explain or decorate an augmented resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er illustrationer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af billedindhold, som er skabt til at forklare eller udsmykke den berigede ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illustrations for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is augmented by pictorial content designed to explain or decorate it.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er illustrationer til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er beriget med billedindhold, som er skabt til at forklare eller udsmykke den.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has illustrative content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an indication of the kinds of image content that supplement the main resources that are embodied by an augmentation aggregate.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har illustrativt indhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en tilstedeværelse af billedindhold, der medfølger en ressources primære indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is imitated as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that copies the style or content of another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er efterlignet som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der kopierer en oprindelig ressources stil eller indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is imitation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose style or content is copied in a derivative resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er imitation af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, hvis stil eller indhold er kopieret i en afledt ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has immediate source of acquisition of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the circumstances under which a resource is directly acquired, including a method, source, and date of acquisition.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har direkte anskaffelseskilde for eksemplar
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en kilde, hvorfra institutionen har anskaffet en ressource, samt de omstændigheder under hvilke det blev modtaget.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has incidental music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource that complements a resource that is a play or other resource for the stage that is realized as spoken word.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er skuespilsmusik
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en musikressource, der indeholder tilhørende musik til et skuespil eller anden ressource for et talt sceneværk.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is incidental music for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a play or other resource for the stage that is realized as spoken word and that is complemented by a musical resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er skuespilsmusik til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, såsom et skuespil eller et andet talt sceneværk, der anvender en ressource til et musikværk som tilhørende musik.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has index
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that provides a systematic, alphabetical guide to the contents of another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indeks
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der indeholder en systematisk, alfabetiseret oversigt over indholdet i hovedværket, normalt kædet sammen med sidenumre eller andre henvisningskoder.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is indexed in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is an abstracting and indexing service that indexes the contents of another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indekseret i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er en abstracts- og indekseringsservice, der indekserer en oprindelig kildes indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is indexing for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose contents have been indexed by a related resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indeksering for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, hvis indhold er blevet indekseret af en abstract- og indekseringsservice.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is index to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is used as a basis for a resource that is a systematic, alphabetical guide to its contents.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indeks til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er anvendt som grundlag for et indeks, dvs. en systematisk, alfabetiseret oversigt over indholdet i hovedressourcen, normalt kædet sammen med sidenumre eller andre henvisningskoder.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has inscriber
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who has written a statement of dedication or gift on a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har dedikationsskriver
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har skrevet en tilegnelses- eller gavekommentar på en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is inscriber of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for inscribing a text, such as a statement of dedication or gift.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er dedikationsskriver i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der har skrevet en dedikations- eller gaveangivelse på en ressource til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has insert
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a separate part of another resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indlæg
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af separat udgivet materiale, der ikke er en integreret del af den større manifestation, som den er indlagt i.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is inserted in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource into which material is inserted that is not an integral part of the publication.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indlagt i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, hvori der er indlagt materiale, der ikke er en integreret del af publikationen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is inspiration for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that was inspired by a related resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er inspiration til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der var inspireret af en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is inspired by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that serves as the inspiration for a related resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er inspireret af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der tjener som inspiration for en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is instructor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of teaching or providing a demonstration.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er lærer i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en udøver, der bidrager til en ressource ved at give instruktion eller demonstration til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has instrumental conductor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a conductor who contributes to a musical resource by leading an instrumental performing group in a musical or dramatic presentation.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har instrumentaldirigent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en dirigent, der har bidraget til en musikressource ved at lede en optrædende instrumentalgruppe i en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is instrumental conductor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of conducting and leading an instrumental performing group in a musical or dramatic presentation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er instrumentaldirigent i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en dirigent, der har bidraget til en musikressource ved at lede en optrædende instrumentalgruppe i en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation etc. til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has instrumentalist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer who contributes to a resource by playing a musical instrument.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har musiker
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en optrædende, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at spille et musikinstrument.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is instrumentalist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of playing a musical instrument.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musiker i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en udøver der bidrager til en ressource ved at spille et musikinstrument til en ressource

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has intended audience
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a category of user for whom the content of a resource is intended, or for whom the content is considered suitable.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har målgruppe
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en brugerkategori, som en ressources indhold er beregnet for, eller for hvilken indholdet anses passende.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has interactivity mode
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a capacity of content to respond to actions performed by the user.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has interviewee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for creating a resource by responding to an interviewer, usually a reporter, pollster, or some other kind of agent who gathers information.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har interviewede
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have skabt en ressource ved at besvare spørgsmål fra en interviewer, normalt en journalist, medarbejder ved et meningsmålingsinstitut eller en anden informationsindsamler.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is interviewee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of being interviewed, usually by a reporter or some other information gathering agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er interviewet i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have skabt en ressource ved at besvare spørgsmål fra en interviewer, normalt en journalist, medarbejder ved et meningsmålingsinstitut eller en anden informationsindsamler en ressource..

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has interviewer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for creating a resource by acting as an interviewer, reporter, pollster, or some other kind of agent who gathers information.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har interviewer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have skabt en ressource ved at optræde som interviewer, journalist, medarbejder ved et meningsmålingsinstitut eller en anden informationsindsamler.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is interviewer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of interviewing, reporting, or some other information gathering agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er interviewer i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have skabt en ressource ved at optræde som interviewer, journalist, medarbejder ved et meningsmålingsinstitut eller en anden informationsindsamler til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has inventor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for creating a new device or process.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har opfinder
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have skabt en ny anordning eller proces.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is inventor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who is responsible for creating a new device or process to a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er opfinder af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der er ansvarlig for at have skabt en ny anordning eller proces til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has ISSN
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an identifier that is assigned to a series by an ISSN registration agency.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har ISSN for serie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en unik identifikator givet til en serie af en ISSN-registreringsinstitution.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is ISSN of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has an identifier assigned by an ISSN registration agency.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has ISSN of subseries (Deprecated)

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har ISSN for underserie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en unik identifikator givet til en underserie af en ISSN-registreringsinstitution.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has issue
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a static resource that is inspired by the overall editorial policy, scope, and style of a successive aggregating resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er serieindholder af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet udgivet som del af en serie.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is issued with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is issued on the same carrier as a resource being described.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er udgivet sammen med
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er udgivet på den samme bærer som den ressource, der beskrives.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is issue of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a successive aggregating resource that inspires the editorial policy, scope, and style of a static resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er del af serie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, i hvilket en del er blevet udgivet; en titel på en større ressource optræder på delen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has issuing agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who issues a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har ansvarlig institution
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har udgivet en ressource, såsom et officielt skrift fra agenten.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is issuing agent of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for issuing a resource, such as an official organ of the body.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er ansvarlig institution for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har udgivet en ressource, såsom en officiel skrift fra agenten til en ressource.

Relates a resource to a characteristic that applies to the carrier or carriers of the specific early printed resource being described and is assumed not to apply to other resources exemplifying the same resource. includes rubrication, illumination, and other hand colouring, manuscript additions, and binding.
