has jointly held conference
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent that that is a conference that is jointly held with a related conference.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har konference afholdt i fællesskab
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en konference til en konference, der afholdes i fællesskab med en anden konference.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has judge
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who hears and decides on legal matters in court.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har dommer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der hører og træffer beslutning om juridiske anliggender i retten.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is judge of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for hearing and decision on legal matters in court.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er dommer i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der hører og træffer beslutning om juridiske anliggender i retten til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has jurisdiction governed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place that is a jurisdiction to an agent who is a government of a jurisdiction governed by a law, regulation, etc., that was enacted by another government.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har jurisdiktion underlagt
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en jurisdiktion, der har vedtaget en lov, forordning, forfatning, retsplejeregel etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is jurisdiction governed of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a place that is a jurisdiction governed by a law, regulation, etc., that was enacted by another government.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er jurisdiktion underlagt
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en jurisdiktion, der er underlagt en lov, forordning etc., der var vedtaget af en anden domsmyndighed til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has key
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a set of pitch relationships that establishes the tonal centre, or principal tonal centre, used, or intended to be used, for performance of musical content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har toneart
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et sæt af tonehøjdeforhold, der fastlægger et musikressources tonale eller væsentligste tonale centrum.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has key title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a title of resource that is assigned by an ISSN registration agency.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nøgletitel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et unikt navn, der gives til en ressource af et ISSN-registreringsorgan.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is key title of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a title of resource that is assigned by an ISSN registration agency.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has landscape architect
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is an architect who is responsible for creating landscape resources.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har landskabsarkitekt
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en arkitekt, der er ansvarlig for at forme landskaber.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is landscape architect of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for architectural aspects of landscaping.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er landskabsarkitekt til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en arkitekt, der er ansvarlig for at have skabt landskabsressourcer til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has language of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a language an agent uses in its communications, when writing for publication, broadcasting, etc.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har agents sprog
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et sprog en agent anvender til at skrive til publicering, udsendelse etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has language of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a language used for the content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har indholdets sprog
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et sprog, der anvendes til at udtrykke en ressources indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has language version
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is created by changing the language audience of a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is language version of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has a language audience that is changed to create a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has last alphanumeric designation of alternative sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a second or subsequent system of numbering presented in numeric or alphabetic form on the last issue or part of a sequence of numbering for a serial.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har alternativ numerisk og/eller alfabetisk betegnelse for sidste nummer eller del af en sekvens
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et andet eller efterfølgende nummereringssystem i numerisk og/eller alfabetisk form på sidste nummer eller del af nummereringssekvensen for et periodikum.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has last alphanumeric designation of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation in numeric or alphabetic form presented on the last issue or part of a serial issued in a sequence of numbering.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har numerisk og/eller alfabetisk betegnelse for sidste nummer eller del af sekvens
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en betegnelse i numerisk og/eller alfabetisk form på sidste nummer eller del af en nummereringssekvens for et periodikum.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has last chronological designation of alternative sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a second or subsequent system of numbering presented in the form of a date on the last issue or part of a sequence of numbering for a serial.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A designation includes a year; year and month; month, day, and year. A chronological designation of alternative sequence may include a date in a different calendar.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: alternativ kronologisk betegnelse for sidste nummer eller del af en sekvens
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et andet eller efterfølgende nummereringssystem i form af en datering på sidste nummer eller del af nummereringssekvensen for et periodikum.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Betegnelsen omfatter et år; år og måned; måned, dag og år. En alternativ kronologisk betegnelse kan omfatte en dato i en anden kalender.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has last chronological designation of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation in date form presented on the last issue or part of a serial issued in a sequence of numbering.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Designation includes a year; year and month; month, day, and year.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har kronologisk betegnelse for sidste nummer eller del af sekvens
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en betagnelse i form af en datering på sidste nummer eller del af en nummereringssekvens for et periodikum.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Betegnelsen omfatter et år; år og måned; måned, dag og år.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has later title proper (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a title proper appearing on a later issue or part of a multipart monograph or serial that differs from that on the first or earliest issue or part. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har senere hovedtitel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en hovedtitel, der optræder på et senere nummer eller en senere del af et flerbindsværk eller et periodikum, og som afviger fra den titel, der fremgår af første eller tidligste nummer eller del..

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has latitude
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a distance of a point on a planet or satellite measured north and south from the equator.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har breddegrad
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en afstand fra et punkt på en planet eller satellit målt nord og syd fra ækvator.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has layout
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an arrangement of text, images, tactile notation, or other content in a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har layout
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til opstilling af tekst, billeder, taktil notation etc. i en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has letterer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an illustrator who contributes to a comic book, graphic novel, etc., by drawing text and graphic sound effects.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har bogstavtegner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en illustrator, der har bidraget til et udtryk af en tegneserie, en graphic novel etc. ved at tegne teksten og de grafiske lydeffekter.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is letterer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of drawing text and graphic sound effects for a comic book, graphic novel, etc.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bogstavtegner til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en illustrator, der har bidraget til en tegneserie, en graphic novel etc. til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has librettist

rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Authoring of the words of just the songs from a musical is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har librettist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en forfatter af teksten til en opera eller en anden ressource af et musikalsk sceneværk, eller et oratorium.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Omfatter ikke forfatteren til sangteksterne i en musical.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is librettist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for authoring the words of an opera or other musical stage resource, or an oratorio.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er librettist til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en forfatter af ordene til en opera eller anden musikalsk sceneressource, eller et oratorium til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has libretto
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is realized as text that complements a resource that is an opera or other resource for the musical stage, or an oratorio.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er libretto
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der indeholder teksten til en opera eller en ressource til et andet musikalsk sceneværk, eller til et oratorium.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is libretto based on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical or choreographic resource such as an opera, a ballet, or other resource for the musical stage, or an oratorio
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er libretto baseret på
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressouce til en ressource, der er blevet bearbejdet til tekst til en opera eller en anden ressource af et musikalsk sceneværk, eller til et oratorium.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is libretto for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a musical or choreographic resource such as an opera, a ballet, or other resource for the musical stage, or an oratorio, that is complemented by a textual resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er libretto til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en musikressource, såsom en opera eller et andet musikalsk sceneværk, eller et oratorium, der anvender den relaterede ressources tekst.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has lighting designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who contributes to a resource by designing and creating lighting components.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har belysningsdesigner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at designe og skabe belysningsdele.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is lighting designer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of designing and creating lighting components.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er belysningsdesigner for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at designe og skabe belysningsdele til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has lithographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for manufacturing a resource by preparing a stone or plate for lithographic printing.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A lithographer includes a graphic artist creating a design directly on the surface from which printing will be done.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har litograf
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har været involveret i fremstillingen af en ressource ved at forberede en sten eller plade til litografisk trykning.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: En litograf omfatter en grafiker, der har skabt et design direkte på overfladen, hvorfra trykning vil blive lavet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is lithographer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for preparing a stone or plate for lithographic printing.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A lithographer includes a graphic artist creating a design directly on the surface from which printing will be done.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er litograf af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har været involveret i fremstillingen af en ressource ved at forberede en sten eller plade til litografisk trykning til en ressource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: En litograf inkluderer en grafisk artist der har skabt et design direkte på overfladen, hvorfra trykning vil blive lavet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has local affiliate
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a local agent affiliated with a broader agent which acts for it and others at a broader organizational level to an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har lokal filial
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en lokal agent der er tilknyttet et bredere organ som agerer for den og andre på et bredere organisatorisk niveau til en agent.
Relates a resource to a country, state, province, etc., or local place in which an organization has its headquarters. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has location of headquarters (Deprecated)
has longitude
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a distance of a point on a planet or satellite measured east and west from a reference meridian.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har længdegrad
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en afstand fra et punkt på en planet eller satellit målt øst og vest fra referencemeridianen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has longitude and latitude
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a place that identifies the area covered by the cartographic content of a resource using longitude of the westernmost and easternmost boundaries and latitude of the northernmost and southernmost boundaries.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har længdegrad og breddegrad
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et system til identificering af det område, der dækkes af en ressources kartografiske indhold; anvender længdegrader for de vestligste og østligste grænser samt breddegrader for de nordligste og sydligste grænser.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has lyricist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is an author of the words of a popular song, including a song from a musical.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Authoring of just dialogue from a musical is excluded
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har forfatter til sangtekst
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en forfatter til sangteksten til en populær sang, inkl. en eller flere sange fra en musical.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Omfatter ikke forfatteren til dialogen i en musical.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is lyricist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for authoring the words of a popular song, including a song from a musical.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er forfatter til sangtekst til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en forfatter af ordene til en populær sang, inkl. en sang eller flere sange fra en musical til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has lyrics
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a textual resource that complements a musical resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is lyrics for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource that is complemented by a textual resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has makeup artist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who contributes to a resource by applying makeup and prosthetics for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har sminkør
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at lægge makeup og påsætte proteser til en levende billedproduktion eller til en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation eller til underholdning.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is makeup artist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of researching, designing, implementing, or testing software.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sminkør for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at lægge makeup og påsætte proteser til en levende billedproduktion eller til en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation eller til underholdningtil en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource copyright statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about a date that is associated with a claim of protection under copyright or a similar regime.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A copyright date includes a phonogram date that is associated with a claim of protection for an audio recording.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource designation of sequence statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about the designation of a sequence of a resource of a part, issue, or iteration of a diachronic resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource dissertation statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about thesis and other dissertation information.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource distribution statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about data relating to the distribution of a published resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource edition statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about an edition to which a resource belongs.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource frequency statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about an interval at which the resources of parts, issues, or iterations of a diachronic resource are issued.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource identifier statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about a code, number, or other string, usually independent of natural language and social naming conventions, used to identify a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource manufacture statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about data relating to the printing, duplicating, casting, etc., of a published resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource production statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about data relating to the inscription, fabrication, construction, etc., of an unpublished resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource publication statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about the publication, release, or issuing of a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource regional encoding statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about a designation for one or more regions of the world for which a videodisc or video game carrier has been encoded, indicating that playback is restricted to a device configured to decode it.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource series statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about a series to which a resource belongs and a sequence within the series.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about a series that is associated with a resource and a numbering of a resource within the series.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A resource series statement includes any or all of title of series, other title information of series, statement of responsibility relating to series, ISSN, or numbering within sequence.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resource title and responsibility statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource statement about a name of a resource and the agent creating or contributing to the content of the resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A resource title and responsibility statement includes any kind of title or statement of responsibility that is associated with the content of the resource, but does not include a title or statement of responsibility that is associated with an edition, revision or series that is related to the resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has manufacturer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for printing, duplicating, casting, or other method of manufacturing a published resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har producent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for trykning, duplikering, støbning etc. af en ressource i publiceret form.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is manufacturer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for printing, duplicating, casting, etc.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er producent af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der er ansvarlig for trykning, duplikering, støbning etc., til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has manufacture statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a statement that identifies a place of manufacture, a manufacturer, or a date of manufacture of a published resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har produktionsbeskrivelse - publicerede ressourcer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til oplysninger, der identificerer fremstillingssted(er), producent(er) og fremstillingsår eller -dato(er) for en ressource i publiceret form.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A manufacture statement includes a statement about the printing, duplicating, casting, etc., of a published resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has material
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a physical or chemical substance that is used to create a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has media type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a categorization reflecting the general type of intermediation device required to view, play, run, or otherwise access the content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har medietype
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en kategorisering der generelt afspejler typen af formidlingsudstyr/afspiller, der kræves for at tilgå en ressources indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has medium
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who claims to be a channel of communication with a world of spirits.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har medie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent der siges at være en kanal for kommunikation mellem den jordiske verden og en åndevereden.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is medium of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent held to be a channel of communication between the earthly world and a world of spirits to a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er medie i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der siges at være en kanal for kommunikation mellem den jordiske verden og en åndevereden, til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has medium of performance (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an instrument, voice, or ensemble for which a musical resource was originally conceived. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har originalbesætning
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et instrument, en sangstemme og/eller en ensemble som en musikressource oprindeligt blev udtænkt til.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has medium of performance of choreographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a type of performer or group of performers participating, or intended to participate, in a performance of choreographic or non-musical dramatic content.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has medium of performance of musical content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an instrument, voice, or ensemble and the number of parts, performers and hands used, or intended to be used, to perform the musical content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har besætning
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et instrument, en stemme og eller ensemble anvendt, eller påtænkt anvendt, til opførelse af musikindhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has member
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who is a member of an agent to an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har medlem af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der er medlem af en agent til en agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is member of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent of which an agent is a member to an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har medlem af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent som en agent er medlem af til en agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is merged to form
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is formed from a coming together of two or more resources.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er lagt sammen til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er dannet ved at lægge to eller flere ressourcer sammen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has mergee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who merged with a related agent to form a third to an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har sammenlagt korporation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der er sammenlagt med en anden agent for at skabe en tredje agent til en agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is merger of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that came together with one or more other resources to form a new resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammenlægning af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der sammen med en eller flere andre ressourcer danner en ny ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has minute taker
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for recording the minutes of a meeting.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har referent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have taget referat ved et møde.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is minute taker of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of recording the minutes of a meeting.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er referent i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der er ansvarlig for at have taget referat ved et møde til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has mirror site
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is an exact copy of a website, used to reduce network traffic or improve the availability of the content of the original site.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er spejlside
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er en nøjagtig kopi af en hjemmeside, som er anvendt til at reducere netværkstrafik eller forbedre tilgængeligheden af originalsidens indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has mixing engineer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an audio engineer who contributes to the audio content of a resource by manipulating, mixing, and assembling the multiple tracks of a recording.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, resulting in a new resource, are excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har mixingtekniker
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en lydtekniker der bidrager til en ressources lydindhold ved at manipulere, mixe og samle de forskellige lydspor på en optagelse.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing-aktiviteter der væsentligt forandrer originalværkets karakter og indhold og derved resulterer i et nyt værk, er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is mixing engineer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that incorporates a contribution by an agent of manipulating, mixing and assembling the multiple tracks of an audio recording.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, resulting in a new resource, are excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er mixing engineer i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en ressource, der inkorporerer et bidrag til lydindholdet ved at manipulere, mixe og samle en indspilnings forskellige spor.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixingaktiviteter der fortrinsvis ændrer natur og indhold på en oprindelig ressource og derved resulterer i en ny ressource, er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has mode of issuance
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a categorization reflecting whether a resource is issued in one or more parts, the way it is updated, and its intended termination.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har udgivelsesform
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en kategorisering, der afspejler, hvorvidt en ressource er udgivet i en eller flere dele, hvordan den opdateres, og hvorvidt dens ophør er forudbestemt eller ej.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has moderator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer who contributes to a resource by leading a program, often broadcast, where topics are discussed, usually with participation of experts in fields related to the discussion.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har ordstyrer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en optrædende, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at lede et program, ofte transmitteret, hvor emner diskuteres, normalt med deltagelse af fagfolk inden for felter, der er relateret til diskussionen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is moderator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of leading a program, often broadcast, where topics are discussed, usually with participation of experts in fields related to the discussion.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er ordstyrer i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en udøver, der bidrager til en ressource ved at lede et program, ofte transmitteret, hvor emner diskuteres, normalt med deltagelse af fagfolk indenfor felter, der er relateret til diskussionen, til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has modification of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a modification that is specific to a resource and is assumed not to apply to other resources exemplifying the same resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om ressourcespecifikke indholdskarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note om oplysninger om ekstra karakteristika, der er specifikke for en beskreven ressource og der antages ikke at være gyldige for andre ressourcer der eksemplificerere den samme ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is modified by variation as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource in which melodic, thematic, or harmonic material taken from another resource forms a discrete theme, which is repeated one or more times with subsequent modifications.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er ændret ved variation til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en musikressource, hvori melodisk, tematisk eller harmonisk materiale taget fra det oprindelige værk danner et bestemt tema, der gentages en eller flere gange med efterfølgende ændringer.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has modifier
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who makes changes to a resource without creating a new resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is modifier of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that is changed by an agent without creating a new resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is adapted as a motion picture.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er filmatisering af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet bearbejdet som film.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has motion picture music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource that complements a resource that is a motion picture.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er filmmusik
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en musikressource, der er anvendt i en film.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has motion picture screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is textual resource that complements a resource that is a motion picture.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er filmmanuskript
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der indeholder teksten til en film.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture screenplay based on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is adapted as a screenplay for a motion picture.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er filmmanuskript baseret på
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet bearbejdet til manuskript til en film.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has mount
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a physical material used for the support or backing to which the base material of a resource is attached.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har montage / ramme
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et fysisk materiale, der udgør den støtte eller bagbeklædning, som en ressources basismateriale er fastgjort på.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource that complements a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musik
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en musikressource, der er anvendt i en film, et skuespil, et tv-program etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has musical director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who contributes to a resource by coordinating the activities of composers, sound editors, and sound mixers for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har orkesterleder
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til een ressource ved at koordinere komponistens, tonemesterens og lydmixernes aktiviteter ved en levende billedproduktion eller en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation eller i underholdning.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of coordinating the activities of composers, sound editors, and sound mixers for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musikdirektør for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at koordinere komponistens, tonemesterens og lydmiksernes aktiviteter ved en levende billedproduktion eller en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation eller underholdning til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical setting of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that provides text for a non-dramatic musical resource, other than an oratorio.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musiksætning af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der indeholder tekst til en ressource af et ikke-dramatisk musikværk, bortset fra et oratorium.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical theatre adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is adapted as a musical theatre resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musikteaterbearbejdelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet bearbejdet til musikteater-ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to resource that is complemented by a musical resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musik til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource såsom en film, et skuespil, et tv-program etc., der anvender en musikressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for motion picture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a motion picture that is complemented by a musical resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musik til film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der anvender en musikressource i en film.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for radio program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a radio program that is complemented by a musical resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musik til radioprogram
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der anvender en musikressource i et radioprogram.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for television program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a television program that is complemented by a musical resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musik til tv-program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der anvender en musikressource i et tv-program.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for video
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a video that is complemented by a musical resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musik til video
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der anvender en musikressource i en video.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has music programmer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who contributes to a resource by using electronic audio devices or computer software to generate sounds.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har musikprogrammør
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der bidrager til en musikressource ved at bruge elektronisk lydudstyr og/eller computersoftware til at generere lyd.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Skabelse af en ny musikressource er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music programmer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a musical resource that incorporates a contribution by an agent of using electronic audio devices or computer software to generate sounds.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musikprogrammør i

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an appellation of agent in natural language and phrasing used in common discourse.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har agents navn
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et ord, tegn eller gruppe af ord og/eller tegn, som en agent er kendt under.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is name of agent of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an appellation of agent in natural language and phrasing used in common discourse to an agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of distributor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a name of an agent who is responsible for distributing a published resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har distributørnavn
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et navn på agent, der er ansvarlig for distribution af en ressource i publiceret form.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is name of distributor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for distributing a published resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of entity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an entity to an appellation of entity in natural language and phrasing used in common discourse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is name of entity of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to an entity that has an appellation of entity in natural language and phrasing used in common discourse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of manufacturer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a nomen that is a name of an agent who is responsible for printing, duplicating, casting, or other method of manufacturing a published resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har producentnavn
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et navn på agent, der er ansvarlig for trykning, duplikering, støbning etc. af en ressource i publiceret form.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is name of manufacturer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for printing, duplicating, casting, etc., a published resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of place
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to an appellation of place in natural language and phrasing used in common discourse.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har navn på et sted
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et ord, tegn eller gruppe af ord og/eller tegn, som et sted er kendt under.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is name of place of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a place that has a name in natural language and phrasing used in common discourse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of producer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a nomen that is a name of an agent who is responsible for inscribing, fabricating, constructing, or other method of producing an unpublished resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har producers navn
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et navn på agent, der er ansvarlig for indgravering, fremstilling, konstruktion etc. af ressource i upubliceret form.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is name of producer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for inscribing, fabricating, constructing, etc., an unpublished resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of publisher
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a name of an agent who is responsible for publishing, releasing, or issuing a published resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har udgivers navn
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et navn på en agent, der er ansvarlig for at publicere, offentliggøre eller udgive en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is name of publisher of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for publishing, releasing, or issuing a published resources.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of timespan
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a timespan to an appellation of timespan in natural language and phrasing used in common discourse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is name of timespan of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a timespan that has a name in natural language and phrasing used in common discourse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has narrator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is a performer who contributes to a resource by reading aloud or giving an account of an act, occurrence, or other event.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har fortæller/indlæser
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en optrædende, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at læse højt eller berette om en handling, en hændelse, et begivenhedsforløb etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is narrator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an resource that includes a contribution by an agent of reading aloud or giving an account of an act, occurrence, or other event.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er fortæller i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en udøver der bidrager til en ressource ved at læse højt eller berette om en handling, en hændelse, et begivenhedsforløb, etc. til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has nature of content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a specific character of the primary content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har indholdets art
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en specifik egenskab ved en ressources primære indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has nomen string
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to the combination of signs that forms an appellation associated with an entity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a broad unstructured description of one or more attributes of an agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on capture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information associated with the recording, filming, etc., of the content of a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Note on capture includes the circumstances such as a live or studio recording, the equipment used, etc.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om optagelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note der giver oplysninger knyttet til optagelse, indspilning etc. af indholdet af en ressource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Note om optagelse omfatter forhold såsom live- eller studieoptagelse, anvendt udstyr etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on changes in carrier characteristics
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on variations in the carrier characteristics that are found on resources of parts, issues, or iterations of a diachronic resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om ændringer i bærerkarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note om ændringer i bærerens karakteristika, der optræder i efterfølgende numre eller dele af en ressource, der er udgivet i successive dele, eller mellem iterationer af en integrerende ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on changes in content characteristics
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on variations in the content characteristics of parts, issues, or iterations of a diachronic resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om ændringer i bærerkarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note om ændringer i bærerens karakteristika, der optræder i efterfølgende numre eller dele af en ressource, der er udgivet i successive dele, eller mellem iterationer af en integrerende ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on copyright date
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on a copyright date.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om copyrightår
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om copyrightår, der ikke er registreret som en del af copyrightangivelsen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on dimensions of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on the dimensions of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om ressources størrelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om en ressources størrelse, der ikke er registreret som en del af størrelsesangivelsen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on distribution statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on the distribution of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til distriubutionsbeskrivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der angiver detaljer om distributionssted, distributør eller distributionsår, eller oplysninger om ændringer i distributionssted, distributør eller distributørnavn.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on edition statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on an edition of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til udgavebeskrivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om kilden til en udgavebeskrivelse, om udgavebeskrivelse relateret til numre, dele etc., om ændringer i udgavebeskrivelse eller om andre oplysninger relateret til en udgavebeskrivelse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on entity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an entity to a broad unstructured description of one or more attributes of an entity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on extent of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on the extent of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om omfang af ressource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om en ressources omfang, der ikke er registreret som en del af omfangsangivelsen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on frequency (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing details on the currency of the contents, on the frequency of release of issues or parts of a serial or the frequency of updates to an integrating resource, or on changes in frequency. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om frekvens
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver detaljer om dækningsperioden, om udgivelsesfrekvensen for numre eller dele af et periodikum eller opdateringsfrekvensen for en integrerende ressource eller ændringer i frekvens.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on identifier for resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on an identifier for a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om identifikator for ressourcen
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om identifikatorer for ressourcen, der ikke fremgår af identifikatorangivelsen for ressourcen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on issue, part, or iteration used as basis for identification of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that identifies an issue or part of a multipart monograph or serial, or an iteration of an integrating resource that has been used as a basis for the identification of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om nummer, del eller iteration, anvendt som grundlag for identifikation af ressource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der identificerer et nummer eller en del af et flerbindsværk eller et periodikum, eller en iteration af en integrerende ressource, der er brugt som grundlag for identifikation af en ressource.
Relates a resource to an annotation providing additional information about resource or resource attributes. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on manifestation or item (Deprecated)
has note on manufacture statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on the manufacture of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til produktionsbeskrivelse - publicerede ressourcer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver detaljer om fremstillingssted, producent eller fremstillingsår, eller om ændringer i fremstillingssted, producent eller producentnavn.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on numbering of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on the range of designators that is used to indicate a sequence of the individual parts or iterations of a resource.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om nummereringen af første og/eller sidste nummer eller del, om kompleks eller uregelmæssig nummerering (inkl. nummereringsfejl), om den periode, der dækkes af et bind, et nummer, en del etc., eller om andre oplysninger relateret til nummerering af periodika.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on production statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on the production of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til produktionsbeskrivelse - upublicerede ressourcer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver detaljer om produktionssted, producer eller produktionsår, eller om ændringer i produktionssted, producer eller producernavn.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on publication statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on the publication of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til publiceringsbeskrivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver detaljer om publiceringssted, udgiver eller publiceringsår eller oplysninger om ændringer i publiceringssted, udgiver eller udgivernavn, eller om ophør af publicering.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a broad unstructured description of one or more attributes of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til ressource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver supplerende oplysninger om indhold, der er registreret, som et attribut til udtrykket.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on series statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on a series with which a resource is associated.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til seriebeskrivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om kompleks seriebetegnelse eller ukorrekt nummerering i serien, om ændringer i seriebeskrivelse eller om andre oplysninger relateret til seriebeskrivelsen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on statement of responsibility
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to note on resource that provides information on an agent, and their function, who is responsible for a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til ophavsangivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om en agent, der ikke er nævnt i ophavsangivelsen, men som er tillagt ansvaret for det intellektuelle eller kunstneriske indhold af værket, om variantformer af navne, der optræder i ressourcen, om ændringer i ophavsangivelser eller om andre detaljer der knytter sig til ophavsangivelsen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on resource that provides information on inaccuracies appearing in titles, complex changes in titles, or on other information relating to a title.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om titel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om titlens kilde, den dato, hvor titlen blev set, titelvariationer, unøjagtigheder, sletninger etc. eller om andre oplysninger relateret til en titel.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is novelization of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is adapted as a novel.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er omskrivning til roman af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet bearbejdet som roman.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering of part
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation in the form of numbers or alphabetic characters, or a date or other timespan, that is used to indicate a sequence of a part resource within a whole resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Numbering may consist of a numeral, a letter, any other character, or the combination of these with or without an accompanying caption, and/or a chronological designation.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nummerering af del
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en sekvensbetegnelse for en del eller flere dele i et større Ressource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Nummerering af del kan omfatte et tal, et bogstav, ethvert andet tegn eller en kombination af disse med eller uden tilhørende tekst og/eller en kronologisk betegnelse

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the first and last designations of a sequence of the individual parts or iterations of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nummerering af periodika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en betegnelse for hvert nummer eller hver del af et periodikum.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Nummerering af omfatter et tal, et bogstav, ethvert andet tegn eller en kombination af disse med eller uden tilhørende tekst og/eller en kronologisk betegnelse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering within sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation of a sequencing of a part or parts within a series.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Numbering may include dates or other timespans, alphanumeric or other characters, and an accompanying caption.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nummerering indenfor serie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en sekvensbetegnelse for en del eller flere dele i en serie.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Nummerering omfatter et tal, et bogstav, ethvert andet tegn eller en kombination af disse med eller uden tilhørende tekst og/eller en kronologisk betegnelse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering within subseries (Deprecated
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation of a sequencing of a part or parts within a subseries. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Numbering may consist of a numeral, a letter, any other character, or the combination of these with or without an accompanying caption and/or a chronological designation. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nummerering indenfor underserie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en sekvensbetegnelse for en del eller flere dele i en underserie.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Nummerering omfatter et tal, et bogstav, ethvert andet tegn eller en kombination af disse med eller uden tilhørende tekst og/eller en kronologisk betegnelse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has number of conference
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation of a sequencing of a conference, etc., within a series of conferences, etc.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nummer på konference etc.
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en sekvensbetegnelse etc. i en række af konferencer etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numeric designation of musical resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a serial number, opus number, or thematic index number assigned to a musical resource by a composer, publisher, or a musicologist.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A numeric designation of a musical resource includes a caption such as e.g., no., op., BWV, and it may include a numeral, a letter, a word, any other character, or the combination of these.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har numerisk betegnelse for musikressource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et serienummer, opusnummer eller værkfortegnelsesnummer tildelt en musikressource af en komponist, en udgiver eller en musikforsker.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: En numerisk betegnelse for en musikressource inkluderer en indledning som fx no., op., BWV og den kan inkludere et nummer, et bogstav, et ord, eller et hvilket som helst andet tegn eller en kombination af disse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is numeric designation of musical resource of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a musical resource that has an identifier for resource that is a serial number, opus number, or thematic index number assigned to a musical resource by a composer, publisher, or a musicologist.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has officer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent holding an office in or commanding an agent to an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har embedsmand
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der har et embede i en ledelse eller der leder en agent til en agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has officer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent holding an office in or commanding an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er embedsmand i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en agent hvor en agent har et embede eller som en person leder.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is on disc with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is contained on the same disc as a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er på disc med
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er udgivet på den samme disc som en ressource, der beskrives.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has onscreen participant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who contributes to a nonfiction moving image resource by taking an active role as a participant.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Appearance on screen to provide contextual or background information is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har programmedvirkende
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer et udtryk til en agent, der har bidraget til en levende billed-ressource af faktuel karakter ved at påtage sig en aktiv rolle som deltager.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Optræden på skærmen for at give kontekstuel eller baggrundsinformation er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is onscreen participant of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of taking an active role as a participant.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Appearance on screen to provide contextual or background information is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er programmedvirkende i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har bidraget til en levende non-fiction billed-ressource ved at påtage sig en aktiv rolle som deltager til en ressource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Optræden på skærmen for at give kontekstuel eller baggrundsinformation er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has onscreen presenter
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer who contributes to a resource by appearing on screen to provide contextual or background information. an on-screen presenter may appear in nonfiction moving image materials or in introductions to fiction moving image materials.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Appearance in nonfiction moving image materials or in introductions to fiction moving image materials is included. Appearance on screen in a non-performing role is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har programvært
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en performer, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at vise sig på skærmen for at give kontekstuel eller baggrundsinformation.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Optræden i levende billedmaterialer af faktuel karakter eller i introduktioner til levende billedmaterialer af fiktiv karakter er omfattet. Optræden på skærmen i en ikke-fremførende rolle er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is onscreen presenter of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer who contributes to a resource by appearing on screen to provide contextual or background information. an on-screen presenter may appear in nonfiction moving image materials or in introductions to fiction moving image materials to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Appearance in nonfiction moving image materials or in introductions to fiction moving image materials is included. Appearance on screen in a non-performing role is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er programvært på skærmen i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en udøver, der bidrager til en ressource ved at optræde på en skærm for at give kontekstuel- eller baggrundsinformation til en ressource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: En programvært kan optræde i levende billedmaterialer af faktuel karakter eller i introduktioner til levende billedmaterialer af fiktiv karakter. Optræden på skærmen i en ikke-optrædende rolle er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is opera adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is adapted as an opera.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er operabearbejdelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet bearbejdet til opera.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has opus number
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a numeric designation of musical resource assigned from a list of resources of a composer indicating the chronological order of composition.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is opus number of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a musical resource that has an identifier for resource that is a numeric designation assigned from a list of resources of a composer indicating chronological order of composition.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is oratorio adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is adapted as an oratorio.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er oratoriebearbejdelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet bearbejdet som et oratorium.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has organizer
