rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har publiceringsbeskrivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til oplysninger, der identificerer publiceringssted(er), udgiver(e) og år eller dato(er) for publiceringen af en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has publisher
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for publishing, releasing, or issuing a published resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har udgiver
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for at publicere, offentliggøre eller udgive en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has publisher number for notated music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a numbering designation assigned to a notated music resource by a publisher.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A publisher number for notated music sometimes includes initials, abbreviations, or words identifying the publisher.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har udgivers editionsnummer for noteret musik
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en nummereringsbetegnelse givet til en noteret musikressource af en udgiver.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Editionsnummer for noteret musik indeholder sommetider initialer, forkortelser eller ord der identificerer udgiveren.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is publisher number for notated music of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a numbering designation assigned to a notated music resource by a publisher.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The number normally appears only on the title page, the cover, or the first page of music, and sometimes includes initials, abbreviations, or words identifying the publisher.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is publisher of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for publishing, releasing, or issuing.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er udgiver af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der er ansvarlig for at publicere, offentliggøre eller udsende en ressource til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has puppeteer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer who contributes to a resource by manipulating, controlling, or directing puppets or marionettes in a moving image production or a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har dukkefører
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en optrædende, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at manipulere, kontrollere eller styre dukker eller marionetter i en levende billedproduktion eller en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation eller i underholdning.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is puppeteer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of manipulating, controlling, or directing puppets or marionettes in a moving image production or a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er dukkefører i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en udøver der bidrager til en ressource ved at manipulere, kontrollere, eller føre dukker eller marionetter i en levende billedproduktion eller en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation eller underholdning til en ressource

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is radio adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is adapted as a radio program.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er radiobearbejdelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet bearbejdet til et radioprogram.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has radio director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is a director who is responsible for the general management and supervision of a radio program.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har radioinstruktør
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en instruktør, der er ansvarlig for ledelse af og tilsyn med et radioprogram.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is radio director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for the general management and supervision of a radio program.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er radioinstruktør af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en instruktør der er ansvarlig for ledelse og tilsyn med et radioprogram til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has radio producer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is a producer who is responsible for most of the business aspects of a radio program.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har radioproducer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en producer, der er ansvarlig for størstedelen af de forretningsmæssige aspekter ved et radioprogram.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is radio producer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for most of the business aspects of the production of a radio program.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er radioproducer af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en producer der er ansvarlig for størstedelen af de forretningsmæssige aspekter ved et radioprogram, til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has radio program music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource that complements a resource that is a radio program.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er radioprogrammusik
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en musikressource, der er anvendt i et radioprogram.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has radio script
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is texual resource that complements a work that is a radio program.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er radiomanuskript
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der indeholder teksten til et radioprogram.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is radio script based on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is adapted as a script for a radio program.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er radiomanuskript baseret på
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet bearbejdet som manuskript til et radioprogram.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has rapporteur
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is an author who is appointed by an organization to report on the proceedings of its meetings.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Responsibility limited to taking minutes is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har rapportør
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en forfatter, der er udpeget af en organisation til at rapportere om udviklingen af dens møder.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Omfatter ikke ansvar begrænset til at tage referat.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is rapporteur of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for reporting on the proceedings of meetings of an organization.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er rapportør af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en forfatter, der er udpeget af en organisation til at rapportere om udviklingen af dens møder til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has real identity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a real agent who assumes an alternate identity to an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har virkelig identitet
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en virkelig agent der antager en alternativ identitet til en agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is real identity of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to an agent who has an appellation of agent that is a real identity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has recording engineer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who contributes to a resource by supervising the technical aspects of a sound or video recording session.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har indspilningstekniker
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en lydtekniker, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at føre tilsyn med de tekniske aspekter af en lyd- eller videooptagelse.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is recording engineer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of supervising the technical aspects of the audio content of a recording session.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indspilningstekniker for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en lydtekniker, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at føre tilsyn med de tekniske aspekter af en optagelsessession til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has recording medium
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a type of medium used to record sound on an audio carrier.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har optagemedie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en type af medie, der er anvendt til at optage lyd på en lydbærer.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has recording source
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a source of information for a metadata resource that is an unstructured description transcribed from a resource being described.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has recordist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who contributes to a resource by using a recording device to capture sound or video during a recording session.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har tonemester
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at anvende et optageudstyr til lyd og/eller video under en optagelse, inkl. feltoptagelser af naturlige lyde, folkloristiske begivenheder, musik etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is recordist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of using a recording device to capture sound or video during a recording session, including field recordings of natural sounds, folkloric events, music, or other performances.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er tonemester for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at anvende et optageudstyr til at fange lyd og/eller video under en optagelsessession, inkl. feltoptagelser af naturlige lyde, folkloristiske begivenheder, musik etc. til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has reduction ratio
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a numerical ratio of the size of a micro-image in relation to an original from which it was produced.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har reduktionsforhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et numerisk forhold for størrelsen på et mikrobillede i forhold til den original, som det er fremstillet ud fra.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has reduction ratio designation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a general designation of the size of a micro-image in relation to an original from which it was produced.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har reduktionsforholdsbetegnelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en almindelig betegnelse for størrelsen på et mikrobillede i forhold til den original, som det er fremstillet ud fra.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has reference source
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource which provides evidence for the use of a nomen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has referential resource relationship with (Deprecate)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that references a related resource. (Deprecated)
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har henvisende ressourcerelation med
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource der henviser til en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has regional encoding
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation for one or more regions of the world for which a videodisc or video game carrier is encoded, indicating that playback is restricted to a device configured to decode it.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har regional kodning
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en kode, der identificerer den region i verden, som en videodisc er kodet til, og som forhindrer, at videodiscen bliver spillet på en afspiller solgt i en anden region.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has regional version
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is created by changing the regional audience of a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is regional version of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has a regional audience that is changed to create a resource.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent who is associated with an agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har relateret agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er knyttet til en beskreven ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related agent of entity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an entity to an agent who is associated with an entity.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to an agent who is associated with a nomen.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to an agent who is associated with a place.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related agent of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is associated with a resource.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a timespan to an agent who is associated with a timespan.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an entity that is associated with an agent.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an entity to an entity that is associated with an entity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related entity of nomen
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to an entity that is associated with a nomen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related entity of place
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to an entity that is associated with a place.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related entity of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an entity that is associated with a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related entity of timespan
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a timespan to an entity that is associated with a timespan.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related nomen of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an nomen that is associated with an agent.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an entity to a nomen that is associated with an entity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related nomen of nomen
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a nomen that is associated with a nomen.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to a nomen that is associated with a place.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related nomen of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a nomen that is associated with a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related nomen of timespan
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a timespan to a nomen that is associated with a timespan.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related place of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a place that is associated with an agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related place of entity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an entity to a place that is associated with an entity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related place of nomen
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a place that is associated with a nomen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related place of place
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to a place that is associated with a place.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related place of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a place that is associated with a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related place of timespan
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a timespan to a place that is associated with a timespan.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related resource of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to resource that is associated with an agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related resource of entity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an entity to a resource that is associated with an entity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related resource of nomen
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to resource that is associated with a nomen.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related resource of place
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to resource that is associated with a place.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related resource of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is associated with a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har relateret ressource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der knytter sig til en beskreven ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related resource of timespan
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a timespan to a resource that is associated with a timespan.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a timespan that is associated with an agent.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to a timespan that is associated with a place.

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a timespan to a timespan that is associated with a timespan.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is remade as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a motion picture, radio program, television program, or video based on an earlier resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er genindspillet som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource af en film, et radio- eller tv-program eller en video baseret på en tidligere ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is remake of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a new motion picture, radio program, television program, or video.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er genindspilning af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er anvendt som grundlag for en ny film, et nyt radioprogram, et nyt tv-program eller en ny video.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has remix artist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is responsible for creating an audio resource by manipulating, recombining, mixing, and reproducing previously recorded sounds.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that do not substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, and mixing recorded tracks together to appear as one continuous track are excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har remixer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent ansvarlig for at skabe en lydressource ved at manipulere, rekombinere, mixe og reproducere tidligere indspillede lyde.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remix-aktiviteter der ikke væsentligt ændrer natur og indhold på originalværket, og mixning af indspillede lydspor til at fremstå som et uafbrudt spor er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is remix artist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for manipulating, recombining, mixing, and reproducing previously recorded sounds.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that do not substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, and mixing recorded tracks together to appear as one continuous track are excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er remixer til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en lydressource, skabt ved at manipulere, rekombinere, mixet og reproducere tidligere indspillede lyde.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixaktiviteter der ikke væsentligt ændrer natur og indhold på den oprindelige ressource, og miksning af indspillede lydspår til at fremstå som et uafbrudt spor ekskluderes.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replaced by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content supersedes and renders obsolete the content of another resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to single-part units, multipart monographs, and integrating resources.
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en senere ressource, der er anvendt delvist i stedet for en tidligere ressource, normalt fordi den senere ressource indeholder opdateret eller ny information, der betyder, at den tidligere ressource er forældet.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Den her relation bruges generelt til enkeltstående monografier, flerbindsværker og integrerende ressourcer.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replaced in part by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content partially supersedes and renders obsolete the content of another resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to single-part units, multipart monographs, and integrating resources.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er delvis erstattet af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en senere ressource, der er delvist anvendt i stedet for et tidligere udtryk, normalt fordi den senere ressource indeholder opdateret eller ny information, der betyder, at den tidligere ressource er forældet.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation anvendes generelt til enkeltstående monografier, flerbindsværker og integrerende ressourcer.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replacement in part of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content is partially superseded and rendered obsolete by the content of another resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This element applies in general to a static resource or an integrating resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er delvis erstatning af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en tidligere ressource, hvis indhold er blevet delvist erstattet af en senere ressource, normalt fordi den senere ressource indeholder opdateret eller ny information, der betyder, at den tidligere ressource er forældet.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation anvendes generelt til enkeltstående monografier, flerbindsværker og integrerende ressourcer.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replacement of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content is superseded and rendered obsolete by the content of another resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This element applies in general to a static resource or an integrating resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er erstatning af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en tidligere ressource, hvis indhold er blevet erstattet af en senere ressource, normalt fordi den senere ressource indeholder opdateret eller ny information, der betyder, at den tidligere ressource er forældet.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation anvendes generelt til enkeltstående monografier, flerbindsværker og integrerende ressourcer.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reprinted as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that reissues the same resource as a printed resource being described.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er genoptrykt som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der genudgiver den samme ressource som en trykt beskreven ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reprint of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that reissues the same resource as a printed resource being described.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er genoptryk af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en trykt ressource, der er anvendt som grundlag for en genudgivelse af en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reproduced as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that reproduces a related resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er reproduceret som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er en reproduktion af en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reproduction of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is used as a basis for a reproduction.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er reproduktion af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er anvendt som grundlag for en reproduktion.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has researcher
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who does research in support of the creation of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har researcher
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der udfører forskning til støtte for skabelsen af en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is researcher of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility of an agent for research in support of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er researcher for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der udfører forskning til støtte for skabelsen af en ressource til en ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has research supervisor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an academic supervisor who is responsible for advising or supervising research that results in a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is research supervisor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility as an academic supervisor of research that results in a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has resolution
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a clarity or fineness of detail in a digital image, expressed by a measurement of the image in pixels, etc.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har opløsning
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et digitalt billedes skarphed eller finhedsgrad, udtrykt som en måling af pixels i et billede etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has respondent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is a candidate for a degree who defends or opposes a thesis provided by the praeses in an academic disputation.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har respondent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en kandidat til en akademisk grad, der forsvarer eller opponerer mod en tese, der er fremsat af præses i et akademisk afhandlingsforsvar.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is respondent of

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sceneinstruktør af

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has statement of responsibility relating to title proper
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a statement associated with a title proper of a resource that relates to an identification or function of agents responsible for the creation of, or who contributes to a realization of, the intellectual or artistic content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har ophavsangivelse relateret til hovedtitel

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has static version

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har kunstnerisk fortæller

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is storyteller of

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er historiefortæller i

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has student

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is student at

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has subject

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is subject of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is about a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er emne i

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has subseries

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er underserie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en serie eller et flerbindsværk der konsekvent optræder i en større ressource; en titel på en større ressource optræder på alle udgaver eller dele af underserien.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is subseries of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a successive aggregating resource that inspires the editorial policy, scope, and style of another successive aggregating resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is succeeded by

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er efterfulft af

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has successor

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har efterfølger

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has summarization of content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an abstract, summary, synopsis, or other description of the content of a resource.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har opsummering af indhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et abstrakt, et resumé, en synopsis etc. af en ressources indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is summarized as

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er opsummeret som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af en kortfattet gengivelse af en oprindelig ressources indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is summary of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a brief recapitulation of its content.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er resume af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er anvendt som grundlag for en kortfattet sammenfatning af dens indhold.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has supplement

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er supplement

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has supplementary content

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har supplerende indhold

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is supplement to

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er landmåler i

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has teacher
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent who instructs a related agent.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har lærer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en agent, der underviser en anden agent.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har lærer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en optrædende, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at give instruktion eller en demonstration.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is thematic index number of

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has title

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har titel

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har ressourcetitel

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is title of resource of

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a name of a series appearing on a resource of a part of a series.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har hovedtitel for underserie

has track configuration

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has transcriber

rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Transcription of a musical resource for a different instrument or performing group is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nedskriver
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource af et værk ved at nedskrive eller notere uskrevet eller ikke-noteret indhold, eller ved at ændre det fra et notationssystem til et andet.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Afskrift af en musikressource for et andet instrument, eller optrædende gruppe, er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is transcriber of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that includes a contribution by an agent of writing down or notating previously unwritten or unnotated content, or by changing it from one system of notation to another.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Transcription of a musical resource for a different instrument or performing group is excluded.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er afskriver af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at nedskrive eller notere uskrevet eller ikke-noteret indhold, eller ved at ændre det fra et notationssystem til et andet til en ressource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Afskrift af en musikressource for et andet instrument eller optrædende gruppe er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has transformation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is created by changing the scope or editorial policy, the genre or literary form, the target audience, or the style of a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has transformation by audience
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is created by changing the audience of a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is transformation by audience of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has an audience that is changed to create a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has transformation by extension plan
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is created by changing the extension plan of a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is transformation by extension plan of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has an extension plan that is changed to create a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has transformation by genre
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is created by changing the genre or literary form of a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is transformation by genre of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has a genre that is changed to create a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has transformation by policy
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is created by changing the scope or editorial policy of a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is transformation by policy of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has a policy that is changed to create a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has transformation by style
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is created by changing the style of a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is transformation by style of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has a style that is changed to create a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is transformation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has a scope or editorial policy, genre or literary form, target audience, or style that is changed to create a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is translated as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that translates the text of another resource into a different language.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er oversat til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der oversætter det oprindelige udtryks tekst til et andet sprog end det, der er anvendt i den originale ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is translation of

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er oversættelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet oversat, dvs. teksten er udtrykt i et andet sprog end det, der er anvendt i den originale ressource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has translator

rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Translation of linguistic content between forms of the same language from different time periods is included.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har oversætter
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at udtrykke en ressources sproglige indhold på et andet sprog end det, der er anvendt i tidligere udtryk af en oprindelige ressource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Oversættelse af sprogligt indhold mellem former af det samme sprog fra forskellige tidsperioder er omfattet.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is translator of

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a timespan that has an access point for timespan that is not selected for preference in a specific vocabulary encoding scheme.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is beginning of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a timespan to a timespan that starts at the time that is a timespan.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is coordinates of cartographic content of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to a resource that is a cartographic resource that has an area of coverage that is described using a mathematical system to identify its boundaries or location.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is ending of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a timespan to a timespan that finishes at the time that is a timespan.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is fuller form of name of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to an agent who has a fuller form of a name or part of a name represented by an initial, abbreviation, or shortened or otherwise modified form.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is given name of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to an agent who uses a name given at birth or at some later point in addition to, or instead of, a surname.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has instructor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is a performer who contributes to a resource by teaching or providing a demonstration.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has intended audience of nomen
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a class of users for which a nomen is intended.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has language of nomen
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a language of an appellation.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has location
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to a delimitation of the physical territory of the place.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is longitude and latitude of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to a resource that is a cartographic resource that has an area of coverage that is identified using longitude of the westernmost and easternmost boundaries and latitude of the northernmost and southernmost boundaries.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of agent of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a nomen that is a name of an agent who is responsible for distributing, printing, duplicating, casting, publishing, releasing, issuing, etc., a published resource, or inscribing, fabricating, constructing, etc., an unpublished resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is name of agent of resource of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a name of agent who is responsible for distribution, printing, duplication, casting, publication, release, issue, etc., or inscription, fabrication, construction, etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is parallel title of series of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a title of series in another language or script.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has place of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a place that is associated with the distribution, printing, duplicating, casting, publication, release, or issuing, etc., of a published resource, or the inscription, fabrication, construction, etc., of an unpublished resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is place of resource of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to a resource that is a published resource that is distributed, printed, duplicated, cast, published, released, or issued, etc., or an unpublished resource that is inscribed, fabricated, constructed, etc., in a place.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reference source of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a nomen for which evidence of use is provided by a resource.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is right ascension and declination of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to a resource that is a cartographic resource that locates a celestial body that is the coverage of the resource and is identified using the angles of right ascension and declination.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is strings of coordinate pairs of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to a resource that is a cartographic resource that has an area of coverage that is identifiedy by a polygon using coordinates for each vertex.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is surname of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to an agent who uses a family name.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is first alphanumeric designation of alternative sequence of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a designation in the form of numbers or alphabetic characters that is used to indicate the first in a concurrent sequence of numbering of parts or iterations.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is first alphanumeric designation of sequence of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a designation in the form of numbers or alphabetic characters that is used to indicate the first in a sequence of numbering of parts or iterations.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is first chronological designation of alternative sequence of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a designation in the form of a date or other timespan that is used to indicate the first in a concurrent sequence of numbering of parts or iterations.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is first chronological designation of sequence of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a designation in the form of a date or other timespan that is used to indicate the first in a sequence of numbering of parts or iterations.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is last alphanumeric designation of alternative sequence of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a designation in the form of numbers or alphabetic characters that is used to indicate the last in a concurrent sequence of numbering of parts or iterations.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is last alphanumeric designation of sequence of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a designation in the form of numbers or alphabetic characters that is used to indicate the last in a sequence of numbering of parts or iterations.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is last chronological designation of alternative sequence of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a designation in the form of a date or other timespan that is used to indicate the last in a concurrent sequence of numbering of parts or iterations.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is last chronological designation of sequence of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a designation in the form of a date or other timespan that is used to indicate the last in a sequence of numbering of parts or iterations.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is numbering within sequence of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a nomen to a resource that has a designation that identifies its position in a sequence of individual parts of a larger resource or parts or issues of a larger resource.
